神奈川県</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"17px\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\" style=\"font-size:17px\">休日の楽しみ：お酒、Netflix、ドライブ、旅行</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"17px\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\" style=\"font-size:17px\">経歴：<br>SESとして1年のアプリ開発経験を経て、Web業界に転職。現在は、ラグジュアリーファッションブランドのEC開発エンジニアとして2年勤務、フロント/バックエンドを主に担当</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"about-en-wrapper\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide about-en-wrapper\"><!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":194,\"mediaLink\":\"http://ranmarusekilocal.local/?attachment_id=194\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":35,\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"className\":\"about-en-wrapper\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center about-en-wrapper\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 35%\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://ranmarusekilocal.local/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ABOUT_EN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\"><!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"bottom\",\"align\":\"full\",\"className\":\"about-en-content\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignfull are-vertically-aligned-bottom about-en-content\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"bottom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"27px\"}},\"className\":\"about-myname base-text\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left about-myname base-text\" style=\"font-size:27px\">RANMARU SEKI</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"17px\"}},\"className\":\"base-text\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left base-text\" style=\"font-size:17px\">Birthday：1995/5/19</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"17px\"}},\"className\":\"base-text\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left base-text\" style=\"font-size:17px\">Birthplace：Kanagawa</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"17px\"}},\"className\":\"base-text\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left base-text\" style=\"font-size:17px\">Hobbies：driving, drinking, traveling, playing piano, watching Netflix</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"17px\"}},\"className\":\"base-text\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left base-text\" style=\"font-size:17px\">Career：<br>A year of experience in application development as SES. Currently working as an e-commerce website development engineer for luxury fashion brands for 2 years, mainly in charge of front / back end.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','ABOUT','','publish','closed','closed','','%e4%bc%9a%e7%a4%be%e6%a6%82%e8%a6%81','','','2022-04-19 23:35:04','2022-04-19 14:35:04','',0,'http://ranmarusekilocal.local/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0);
